				 Car shopping goes online
			The autojunction website. Picture by Kishor Roy Chowdhury																								How about buying your car at the click of a mouse? Auto e-retailing is a reality and fast catching up, if the promoters of www.autojunction.in are to be believed.																								Auto e-retailing can co-exist peacefully and beneficially with the traditional brick and mortar dealership network, each supplementing the other, says Viresh Oberoi, the managing director of mjunction services limited, Indias largest e-commerce company. Autojunction is the auto division of mjunction. It promises to provide end-to-end car buying experience over the Net. One can even book a test drive and get onsite car financing, insurance, accessories, spare parts and service contracts.																								Autojunction has only tied up with Reva Electric Car Company but hopes to have other car majors with them. 						ANASUYA BASU
